lines.text: The only guy I ever had fall for me was an acrobat.
Go into Swing music? No thanks, Dusty, I'll stick to real music.
But look, Amelia, Swing musicians aren't freaks anymore, they're artists with a new mode of music.
A wife should always know where her husband is going in the evening.
You're not annoying me anymore, you're just boring.
Amelia, you said if I came to you on my knees.
I want to kiss you. Won't you let me get up off my knees?
I guess you'll have to because I'll be darned if get down on mine.
